They didn't even need to steal it.

553
00:28:47,870 --> 00:28:49,510
They could just ride it away.

554
00:28:50,290 --> 00:28:51,360
It's all your fault.

555
00:28:51,450 --> 00:28:53,080
Why didn't you tell me it would be gone today?

556
00:28:53,100 --> 00:28:53,620
Call the police.

557
00:28:53,820 --> 00:28:55,300
Why are you blaming me?

558
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:56,670
Calling the police won't help.

559
00:28:56,670 --> 00:28:58,250
There's no surveillance here in this remote area.

560
00:28:58,620 --> 00:28:59,380
We won't get it back.

561
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:01,070
I don't remember this happening.

562
00:29:01,070 --> 00:29:02,270
I don't recall ever losing my bike.

563
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:03,860
People always say,

564
00:29:04,060 --> 00:29:05,620
"Fail in love, succeed in money."

565
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:07,140
How come I'm so unlucky?

566
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:08,110
Don't think about it.

567
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:09,100
Let's go back.

568
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:09,910
I'm not going back.

569
00:29:10,630 --> 00:29:11,860
I want to roam the world.

570
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:12,340
No.

571
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:13,390
I want to travel around China.

572
00:29:14,050 --> 00:29:15,370
But you don't have any transport!

573
00:29:15,410 --> 00:29:16,860
After fighting with Mom like that,

574
00:29:16,860 --> 00:29:18,060
how can you still have the nerve to ask her for money for a motorcycle?

575
00:29:18,060 --> 00:29:19,820
I'll go on foot. I'll hike.

576
00:29:19,820 --> 00:29:20,870
I'm happy.

577
00:29:20,870 --> 00:29:22,100
What's the point of hiking?

578
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:23,220
It's too far.

579
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:24,780
I spent over 200 yuan on a taxi here.

580
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:27,710
Why came to the seaside?

581
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:29,100
It's too far!

582
00:29:29,100 --> 00:29:30,110
Mind your own business.

583
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,100
Look.

584
00:29:32,100 --> 00:29:33,660
I'm really tired.

585
00:29:33,660 --> 00:29:34,860
I've been running around after you every day,

586
00:29:34,860 --> 00:29:35,700
taking care of you.

587
00:29:35,700 --> 00:29:36,710
Coming back is really...

588
00:29:36,710 --> 00:29:38,710
Can you shut up?

589
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:40,790
Fine, I'll shut up.

590
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:42,020
Are you wearing this coat?

591
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:42,990
I'm worried you'll be cold.

592
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:59,350
Hurry up! You're so slow.

593
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:01,170
We've only walked a few kilometers, and you're already done?

594
00:30:01,190 --> 00:30:02,260
With your stamina, you want to hike

595
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:03,110
and travel the world?

596
00:30:03,110 --> 00:30:05,020
Just find a job and earn money.

597
00:30:05,730 --> 00:30:06,540
Do you think

598
00:30:06,820 --> 00:30:08,420
I haven't sent out resumes?

599
00:30:08,810 --> 00:30:11,180
I've sent so many, but they've all gone unanswered.

600
00:30:12,780 --> 00:30:14,140
Wait a minute, wait.

601
00:30:18,220 --> 00:30:20,060
Well, you could ask for my "golden touch".

602
00:30:20,510 --> 00:30:21,860
If you're nice about it,

603
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:23,470
I might consider it.

604
00:30:23,910 --> 00:30:25,050
I'm not walking anymore. I'm done.

605
00:30:26,420 --> 00:30:28,020
Ask you for help?

606
00:30:28,870 --> 00:30:30,420
I will definitely end up homeless.

607
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:33,830
Anyway,

608
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,960
I've got a new body now.

609
00:30:35,990 --> 00:30:37,160
My stamina is great.

610
00:30:38,020 --> 00:30:39,260
You said you didn't want to take a taxi, right?

611
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:40,430
Today we won't take a taxi

612
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:41,360
even if there is any.

613
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,020
We'll just walk.

614
00:30:42,450 --> 00:30:43,730
A road to the end, no turning back.

615
00:30:48,940 --> 00:30:50,380
I've got an idea.

616
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:52,530
You got a new body, huh?

617
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:55,270
We can't let this new body go to waste.

618
00:30:55,740 --> 00:30:57,730
Although I can't touch it,

619
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,890
I can at least ride it!

620
00:31:00,230 --> 00:31:01,260
In your dreams!

621
00:31:01,260 --> 00:31:02,100
No way!

622
00:31:02,990 --> 00:31:04,220
Wait, what are you doing?

623
00:31:04,250 --> 00:31:05,020
Stop right there!

624
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:06,180
I can't walk anymore!

625
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:07,300
What's that got to do with me?

626
00:31:08,530 --> 00:31:09,210
Fine.

627
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,480
If you leave, I'll just lie here and die.

628
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:14,860
Then die.

629
00:31:14,860 --> 00:31:15,860
You've already died once anyway.

630
00:31:15,860 --> 00:31:16,700
One more time won't make a difference.

631
00:31:16,700 --> 00:31:17,830
Just lie where you fall.

632
00:31:17,830 --> 00:31:18,490
Bye-bye.

633
00:31:21,300 --> 00:31:22,580
I'm really not going.

634
00:31:23,430 --> 00:31:27,380
Fine, fine. I'll just die of sunstroke today. Let me die of sunstroke!

635
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:36,490
You're really leaving?

636
00:31:43,570 --> 00:31:44,470
Get off. Off.

637
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:45,900
No way. I've already gotten on.

638
00:31:45,900 --> 00:31:46,820
How could I possibly get off?

639
00:31:47,870 --> 00:31:48,660
Hurry up and go.

640
00:31:50,630 --> 00:31:51,420
You're so annoying.

641
00:31:52,790 --> 00:31:55,730
♫Remember the moments we had♫

642
00:31:55,750 --> 00:31:58,360
♫The ones everyone envied♫

643
00:31:56,700 --> 00:32:00,070
You made me so lost about the future.

644
00:31:58,530 --> 00:32:00,290
♫But later♫

645
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,940
♫But in the end♫

646
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:04,300
You've been away from the workplace for so many years.

647
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:04,160
♫Everything turned to nothing♫

648
00:32:04,300 --> 00:32:05,820
And you still think you can be my future changer?

649
00:32:04,490 --> 00:32:07,230
♫I really wish time would slow down♫

650
00:32:06,230 --> 00:32:08,020
Can't you have a little confidence in your future self?

651
00:32:07,250 --> 00:32:10,580
♫Let me lock away all memories♫

652
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:09,870
You've ended up like this.

653
00:32:09,870 --> 00:32:12,100
How can you expect me to have confidence in myself?

654
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:12,630
♫Laughing and saying♫

655
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,620
Use your naive innocence.

656
00:32:12,650 --> 00:32:16,690
♫I'm fine♫

657
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:15,220
Ignorance is bliss, right?

658
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:22,020
♫Maybe you've forgotten the past♫

659
00:32:20,130 --> 00:32:21,340
What are you doing?

660
00:32:21,900 --> 00:32:23,740
I just want to

661
00:32:23,410 --> 00:32:28,380
♫But I still remember the story♫

662
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:26,220
ride my little motorcycle

663
00:32:26,220 --> 00:32:27,620
and cruise around everywhere.

664
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:29,230
Can we upgrade a bit?

665
00:32:29,230 --> 00:32:30,500
Change it to a four-wheeler.

666
00:32:29,730 --> 00:32:32,870
♫Fall into the whirlpool of memories♫

667
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:31,500
We could even bring Mom along.

668
00:32:32,890 --> 00:32:35,800
♫No matter how time flies♫

669
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,700
That's different.

670
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:35,580
How is it different?

671
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:36,830
We can take turns driving.

672
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:39,380
♫Through the seasons♫

673
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,030
Let Mom sit in the passenger seat.

674
00:32:38,470 --> 00:32:39,660
It'll be awesome, right?

675
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:41,340
Gu Nian, Gu Nian.

676
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:42,430
Gu Nian!

677
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:47,470
♫Trapped in my heart, I'm willing♫

678
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,120
Gu Nian?

679
00:32:44,570 --> 00:32:45,010
No.

680
00:32:47,910 --> 00:32:53,990
♫Even though I know the door isn't locked♫

681
00:32:54,020 --> 00:32:56,260
Gu Nian, you need to keep going.

682
00:32:55,020 --> 00:33:03,530
♫Time, can you not take my story away?♫

683
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:58,130
Our lives are about to

684
00:32:58,950 --> 00:33:00,270
change from this moment.

685
00:33:10,580 --> 00:33:12,380
Why did Tu leave so suddenly?

686
00:33:12,980 --> 00:33:14,620
At least have a farewell meal.

687
00:33:15,460 --> 00:33:17,220
Sometimes letting go is a choice too.

688
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:18,780
Look at Tu,

689
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:20,300
she's off to pursue her future.

690
00:33:20,610 --> 00:33:21,960
Don't you think you should make an effort too

691
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:23,150
and improve yourself?

692
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:24,580
Otherwise, when you meet again,

693
00:33:24,710 --> 00:33:26,110
she'll transform herself and achieve her dreams,

694
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:27,790
and you'll still be stuck in the same old rut.

695
00:33:40,090 --> 00:33:41,150
These three companies

696
00:33:41,470 --> 00:33:43,000
are the ones I interviewed with back then.

697
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:44,500
Each has its pros and cons.

698
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:47,500
This one is the company our computer science department collaborates with.

699
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:48,750
Jiang is working for them.

700
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:50,350
Gao Ren interviewed there too.

701
00:33:53,100 --> 00:33:54,900
This one looks good now,

702
00:33:54,940 --> 00:33:55,960
but seven years from now, it'll be nothing.

703
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:58,220
Here comes the key part:

704
00:33:58,260 --> 00:34:00,450
This one, Fengzhuo Tech,

705
00:34:01,220 --> 00:34:03,220
although it's small now,

706
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,920
will go public in the future.

707
00:34:05,320 --> 00:34:07,480
The rumored behind-the-scenes boss is mysterious and very powerful,

708
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:08,820
and very young,

709
00:34:09,210 --> 00:34:10,170
but no one has seen him.

710
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:14,310
So what do you mean by that?

711
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:16,219
My point is obvious.

712
00:34:16,460 --> 00:34:18,060
We can't just focus on the present.

713
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,960
We need to look long-term.

714
00:34:20,260 --> 00:34:21,909
Grow with a small company

715
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:23,530
can help you reach the top in the future.

716
00:34:24,070 --> 00:34:25,230
You can marry a rich and handsome guy,

717
00:34:25,580 --> 00:34:26,650
become a CEO,

718
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:28,000
and reach the peak of life.

719
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:31,400
So, Fengzhuo Tech

720
00:34:31,429 --> 00:34:32,540
is your best choice.

721
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,940
Not only will you rise as a career newcomer,

722
00:34:35,540 --> 00:34:38,179
but it could also land us a good husband.

723
00:34:41,230 --> 00:34:42,520
Will you go with me then?

724
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:43,830
I can't go.

725
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,909
I have something very important

726
00:34:44,909 --> 00:34:45,699
that I must do.

727
00:34:45,730 --> 00:34:46,409
What is it?

728
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:47,320
Take me with you.

729
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:49,100
I need to go back to my old company

730
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,030
to save people from dire straits.

731
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,380
You shouldn't come along.

732
00:34:51,449 --> 00:34:52,889
Focus on figuring out your own life first.

733
00:34:53,100 --> 00:34:54,710
I understand it pretty well.

734
00:34:55,030 --> 00:34:56,510
Both of us right now:

735
00:34:56,530 --> 00:34:57,560
one is a newcomer,

736
00:34:57,580 --> 00:34:58,780
and the other is a seven-year housewife.

737
00:34:58,810 --> 00:35:00,090
We're almost isolated from the world.

738
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:01,380
What can we possibly

739
00:35:01,380 --> 00:35:02,660
contribute to a startup?

740
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:04,630
We'll be lucky if we're not kicked out.

741
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:07,510
Two burdens still want to be career newcomers?

742
00:35:07,860 --> 00:35:09,110
Why can't our goals

743
00:35:09,110 --> 00:35:10,500
progress together?

744
00:35:10,540 --> 00:35:12,420
This company is full of complicated personnel.

745
00:35:12,450 --> 00:35:13,260
The workplace is treacherous.

746
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,600
I didn't stay long there before.

747
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:15,830
I quit in a fit of anger.

748
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,420
After that, I never went back to work.

749
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:18,620
Now, regretting won't help.

750
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:19,820
You need to be mentally prepared.

751
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:20,820
If it doesn't work out,

752
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,900
we'll switch to Fengzhuo.

753
00:35:22,380 --> 00:35:23,780
You're being too cowardly.

754
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:24,950
You're nothing like me.

755
00:35:24,950 --> 00:35:26,590
The workplace isn't as simple as you think.

756
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:27,420
That's why

757
00:35:27,420 --> 00:35:29,380
we should get back up where we fell.

758
00:35:29,610 --> 00:35:30,570
Besides, Su Yin,

759
00:35:31,470 --> 00:35:32,020
no, wait,

760
00:35:32,530 --> 00:35:35,130
Gu Nian, you're now a cheat code.

761
00:35:35,170 --> 00:35:36,130
You're unbeatable.

762
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:38,390
And last time, it was your own fault.

763
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,860
This time, you've got me.

764
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:42,340
Have you really thought this through?

765
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,680
I want to see

766
00:35:45,990 --> 00:35:48,100
just how scary the company was

767
00:35:48,130 --> 00:35:49,060
that scared me away back then.

768
00:35:49,900 --> 00:35:51,860
You really won't give up until you hit a wall, huh?

769
00:35:51,930 --> 00:35:53,160
So what if I hit a wall?

770
00:35:53,180 --> 00:35:54,500
At worst, I'll just get a bump on my head.

771
00:35:58,070 --> 00:35:59,060
Two Gus working together...

772
00:35:59,390 --> 00:36:00,590
Is invincible.

773
00:36:00,950 --> 00:36:02,150
Let's go to work.

774
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,700
I'm Bai Guo from the Planning Department.
